name: Pricing & Marketing
description:
Looking for a simplified pricing program that won't confuse your customers and increase your sales? See how we use minimum order sessions.
DVD contains layered PSD files and PDF's.
1. All marketing collateral including price card, make up card, phone script card, thank you card, yearbook ad design, consult application and order presentation form.
2. Step by step details of our "Seniors of the Quarter" program. 3. Model release, senior photo session, application, unframed portrait release form.
4. A complete vendor & product list of who we use and which products we sell.

name: Spokesmodel Program
description:
Looking for a successful spokesmodel program that makes money? We have a great program for you. Fischink Photography has over 80 class of 2013 spokesmodels who are all paying clients.
DVD contains layered PSD files and PDF's of
1. All paperwork & marketing material including spokesmodel information packet for all applicants, referral card templates and make up cards.
2. Link to our online spokesmodel application.
3. Our Facebook marketing video specific to spokesmodels.
4. Video of how to put it into action.

name: On-Location Photography
description:
Tired of going over on time during your session or not capturing enough images during your session. Are you shooting to sell? Shooting to minimize retouch? We got your back.
DVD contains layered PSD files and PDF's of.
1. Consult paperwork including model release and senior application.
2. How we schedule on-location sessions.
3. Our "6 rules of approach" for every session".
4. List of our equipment and how we use it.
5. Workflow management with shooting and editing.
6. Software we use and recommended actions.

name: Facebook Marketing
description:
Everyone is saying "Facebook is dead". It is very much alive and we will show you how to bring those seniors in the door with many tools inside Facebook many people are unaware of.
DVD contains video screen shots of.
1. Create a database inside Facebook using lists.
2. Maximize image exposure & tag friends in posts.
3. Finding high school clients on Facebook.
4. Creating Private Groups and working inside them.
5. Creating custom timeline apps on your business page.
6. Video of how to put it into action.
7. PDF of Facebook tips and tricks.

name: Studio on a Stick
description:
Looking for every resource Fischink Photography has used to grow their senior business from 0-200 seniors in less than 5 years, from a corner office in their home to 2 full time studios? Here is our blood, sweat and tears.
Contains everything on the 4 DVDS mentioned above plus 30 days in email support and 1 hour personal phone consult with Ty to help answer your questions.
